{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"運算子","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Expressions_and_Operators_e6fc14473511cf01e7062dfb7751f49d","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>&nbsp;</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"運算子","title":"運算子","isH3":true,"content":"<p>JavaScript 有以下幾種運算子。本節說明運算子，且包含有關運算子優先順序的資訊。</p>\n<ul> <li><a class=\"internal\" href=\"/zh-TW/Core_JavaScript_1.5_教學/運算子/代入運算子\" title=\"zh tw/Core JavaScript 1.5 教學/運算子/代入運算子\">代入運算子</a></li> <li><a class=\"internal\" href=\"/zh-TW/Core_JavaScript_1.5_教學/運算子/比較運算子\" title=\"zh tw/Core JavaScript 1.5 教學/運算子/比較運算子\">比較運算子</a></li> <li><a class=\"internal\" href=\"/zh-TW/Core_JavaScript_1.5_教學/運算子/算術運算子\" title=\"zh tw/Core JavaScript 1.5 教學/運算子/算術運算子\">算術運算子</a></li> <li><a class=\"internal\" href=\"/zh-TW/Core_JavaScript_1.5_教學/運算子/位元運算子\" title=\"zh tw/Core JavaScript 1.5 教學/運算子/位元運算子\">位元運算子</a></li> <li><a class=\"internal\" href=\"/zh-TW/Core_JavaScript_1.5_教學/運算子/邏輯運算子\" title=\"zh tw/Core JavaScript 1.5 教學/運算子/邏輯運算子\">邏輯運算子</a></li> <li><a class=\"internal\" href=\"/zh-TW/Core_JavaScript_1.5_教學/運算子/字串運算子\" title=\"zh tw/Core JavaScript 1.5 教學/運算子/字串運算子\">字串運算子</a></li> <li><a class=\"internal\" href=\"/zh-TW/Core_JavaScript_1.5_教學/運算子/特殊運算子\" title=\"zh tw/Core JavaScript 1.5 教學/運算子/特殊運算子\">特殊運算子</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>JavaScript 有一元和二元兩種運算子，以及特殊的三元運算子，也就是條件運算子。二元運算子需要兩個運算元，一個在運算子之前，一個在運算子之後︰</p>\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">operand1 operator operand2\n</pre>\n<p>例如，<code>3+4</code> 或 <code>x*y</code>。</p>\n<p>一元運算子需要一個運算元，可以運算子之前或之後︰</p>\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">operator operand\n</pre>\n<p>或</p>\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">operand operator\n</pre>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: monospace;\">例如，</span><code>x++</code> 或 <code>++x</code>。</p>\n<h4 id=\"運算子的優先順序\" name=\"運算子的優先順序\">運算子的優先順序</h4>\n<p><small><em>按照<a href=\"/Talk:en/Core_JavaScript_1.5_Guide/Operators#Precedence_Table\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">相關的討論</a>，本表採用<strong>由高到低</strong>的優先順序。</em></small></p>\n<table class=\"fullwidth-table\"> <tbody> <tr> <th>運算子類型</th> <th>單獨的運算子</th> </tr> <tr> <td>成員</td> <td>. &nbsp;[]</td> </tr> <tr> <td>呼叫 / 建立實體</td> <td>() &nbsp;new</td> </tr> <tr> <td>反轉 / 遞增</td> <td>! &nbsp;~ &nbsp;- &nbsp;+ &nbsp;++ &nbsp;-- &nbsp;typeof &nbsp;void &nbsp;delete</td> </tr> <tr> <td>乘法 / 除法</td> <td>* &nbsp;/ &nbsp;%</td> </tr> <tr> <td>加法 / 減法</td> <td>+ &nbsp;-</td> </tr> <tr> <td>位元位移</td> <td>&lt;&lt; &nbsp;&gt;&gt; &nbsp;&gt;&gt;&gt;</td> </tr> <tr> <td>關係</td> <td>&lt; &nbsp;&lt;= &nbsp;&gt; &nbsp;&gt;= &nbsp;in &nbsp;instanceof</td> </tr> <tr> <td>等價</td> <td>== &nbsp;!= &nbsp;=== &nbsp;!==</td> </tr> <tr> <td>位元 AND</td> <td>&amp;</td> </tr> <tr> <td>位元 XOR</td> <td>^</td> </tr> <tr> <td>位元 OR</td> <td>|</td> </tr> <tr> <td>邏輯 AND</td> <td>&amp;&amp;</td> </tr> <tr> <td>邏輯 OR</td> <td>||</td> </tr> <tr> <td>條件</td> <td>?:</td> </tr> <tr> <td>代入</td> <td>= &nbsp;+= &nbsp;-= &nbsp;*= &nbsp;/= &nbsp;%= &nbsp;&lt;&lt;= &nbsp;&gt;&gt;= &nbsp;&gt;&gt;&gt;= &nbsp;&amp;= &nbsp;^= &nbsp;|=</td> </tr> <tr> <td>逗號</td> <td>,</td> </tr> </tbody>\n</table>\n<p><small><strong>表 3.1: 運算子的優先順序</strong></small></p>\n<p>有關本表的詳細版本，且附有關於運算子的完整細節，請參閱 <a class=\"internal\" href=\"/zh-TW/Core_JavaScript_1.5_參考/運算子/運算子的優先順序#%e8%a1%a8\" title=\"zh tw/Core JavaScript 1.5 參考/運算子/運算子的優先順序#表\">參考的章節</a>。</p>\n<p></p><ul class=\"prev-next\">\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/教學/表達式\">« 前頁</a></li>\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/JavaScript/教學/運算子/代入運算子\">次頁  »</a></li>\n</ul><p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"JavaScript 有以下幾種運算子。本節說明運算子，且包含有關運算子優先順序的資訊。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"locale":"en-US","title":"Expressions and operators","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/conflicting/web/javascript/guide/expressions_and_operators_e6fc14473511cf01e7062dfb7751f49d","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/conflicting/web/javascript/guide/expressions_and_operators_e6fc14473511cf01e7062dfb7751f49d/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide","title":"陣列的運用"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Guide/Expressions_and_Operators_e6fc14473511cf01e7062dfb7751f49d","title":"運算子"}],"pageTitle":"運算子 | MDN","noIndexing":true}}